-As the completion of the pyramids in Egypt.

22
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:50,120
We start with the Greek antiquity.

23
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:54,280
Greece is divided into city states.

24
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:59,960
They are independent and consist of a city with surrounding landscapes.

25
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,840
Most are farmers.

26
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:08,360
If they are self -governing - why are we talking about a Greece?

27
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:14,080
Greeks see themselves as a people, regardless of where they bor-

28
