He seems to have been driven by eagerness.

85
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:05,880
A willingness to lower the world.

86
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:11,240
After his death, the kingdom falls apart to the small kingdoms again.

87
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:15,240
However, the expansion leads to Hellenism.

88
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:20,160
It is the mixture between the Greek and the eastern.

89
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:23,520
A typical such mixture is the coin here.

90
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:27,600
A side in Greek and one in Persian style.

91
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:32,480
When it is not war - what is it like in the ancient world?

92
